                  { title: 'Pre-commit to a specific "rescue routine" for each trigger' },
                  { title: 'Practice your recovery plan mentally 3 times before facing real triggers' },
                  { title: 'Set a reminder to review your recovery plan weekly for the first month' },
                  { title: 'If relapse occurs, immediately restart without self-judgment and log the trigger' },
                ],
              },
            ],
          },
          {
            title: 'Replace one keystone habit with a positive alternative that drives cascading improvements',
